### openai-ollama-proxy API quick tests
### Requires VS Code REST Client extension
### Adjust @host if running on a different address

@host = http://host.docker.internal:11434

### ─── Health & Version ───────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Health check (HEAD)
HEAD {{host}}/ HTTP/1.1

###

### Health check (GET)
GET {{host}}/ HTTP/1.1

###

### Version
GET {{host}}/api/version HTTP/1.1

###

### ─── Ollama: Model Management ──────────────────────────────────────────

### List models (tags)
GET {{host}}/api/tags HTTP/1.1

###

### Running models (ps)
GET {{host}}/api/ps HTTP/1.1

###

### Show model info
POST {{host}}/api/show HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "qwen3.6:27b"
}

###

### Pull — simulated progress
POST {{host}}/api/pull HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "llama3.2:1b"
}

###

### Push — simulated progress
POST {{host}}/api/push HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "llama3.2"
}

###

### Create — simulated
POST {{host}}/api/create HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "custom:latest"
}

###

### Copy — simulated
POST {{host}}/api/copy HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "source": "model-a",
  "destination": "model-b"
}

###

### Delete — simulated
DELETE {{host}}/api/delete HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "model-to-delete"
}

###

### ─── Ollama: Chat ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Chat (non-streaming)
POST {{host}}/api/chat HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "qwen3.6:27b",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Say hello in one sentence."}
  ],
  "stream": false
}

###

### Chat (streaming, default)
POST {{host}}/api/chat HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "qwen3.6:27b",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "What is 2+2? Answer briefly."}
  ]
}

###

### Chat with thinking enabled (boolean)
POST {{host}}/api/chat HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "qwen3.6:27b",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "What is the square root of 144? Think step by step."}
  ],
  "stream": false,
  "think": true
}

###

### Chat with thinking level (string: low/medium/high)
POST {{host}}/api/chat HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "qwen3.6:27b",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Solve this puzzle: A bat and a ball cost $1.10..."}
  ],
  "stream": false,
  "think": "high"
}

###

### Chat with auto-injected reasoning effort via model clone (xhigh)
# Uses model-xhigh suffix which auto-injects reasoning_effort=high
POST {{host}}/api/chat HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "qwen3.6:27b-xhigh",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Prove that sqrt(2) is irrational."}
  ],
  "stream": false
}

###

### Chat with auto-injected reasoning effort via model clone (low)
POST {{host}}/api/chat HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "qwen3.6:27b-low",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "What is the capital of France?"}
  ],
  "stream": false
}

###

### Chat with options (temperature, max tokens)
POST {{host}}/api/chat HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "qwen3.6:27b",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Write a haiku about proxies."}
  ],
  "stream": false,
  "options": {
    "temperature": 0.9,
    "num_predict": 50,
    "top_p": 0.95
  }
}

###

### Chat with JSON format
POST {{host}}/api/chat HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "qwen3.6:27b",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Return a JSON object with keys 'name' and 'age' for a fictional character."}
  ],
  "stream": false,
  "format": "json"
}

###

### Chat with tool calling
POST {{host}}/api/chat HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "qwen3.6:27b",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "What is the weather in San Francisco?"}
  ],
  "stream": false,
  "tools": [
    {
      "type": "function",
      "function": {
        "name": "get_current_weather",
        "description": "Get the current weather for a location",
        "parameters": {
          "type": "object",
          "properties": {
            "location": {
              "type": "string",
              "description": "The city and state, e.g. San Francisco, CA"
            }
          },
          "required": ["location"]
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}

###

### Chat with keep_alive (unload)
POST {{host}}/api/chat HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "qwen3.6:27b",
  "messages": [],
  "keep_alive": "0s"
}

###

### ─── Ollama: Generate ──────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Generate (non-streaming)
POST {{host}}/api/generate HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "qwen3.6:27b",
  "prompt": "Say hello in one sentence.",
  "stream": false
}

###

### Generate (streaming)
POST {{host}}/api/generate HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "qwen3.6:27b",
  "prompt": "Count from 1 to 5."
}

###

### Generate with system prompt
POST {{host}}/api/generate HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "qwen3.6:27b",
  "system": "You speak like a pirate.",
  "prompt": "Say hello.",
  "stream": false
}

###

### ─── Ollama: Embeddings ────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Embed (new endpoint)
POST {{host}}/api/embed HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "qwen3.6:27b",
  "input": "Hello, world!"
}

###

### Embeddings (legacy endpoint)
POST {{host}}/api/embeddings HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "qwen3.6:27b",
  "prompt": "Hello, world!"
}

###

### ─── OpenAI Compatible ─────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Models (v1)
GET {{host}}/v1/models HTTP/1.1

###

### Models (no prefix)
GET {{host}}/models HTTP/1.1

###

### Chat completions (non-streaming)
POST {{host}}/v1/chat/completions HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "qwen3.6:27b",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Say hello in one sentence."}
  ]
}

###

### Chat completions (no prefix)
POST {{host}}/chat/completions HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "qwen3.6:27b",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Say hello in one sentence."}
  ]
}

###

### Embeddings (OpenAI format)
POST {{host}}/v1/embeddings HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "qwen3.6:27b",
  "input": "Hello, world!"
}

###

### ─── Anthropic Messages ────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Messages (non-streaming)
POST {{host}}/v1/messages HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: test-key
anthropic-version: 2023-06-01

{
  "model": "qwen3.6:27b",
  "max_tokens": 256,
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Say hello in one sentence."}
  ]
}

###

### Messages (streaming)
POST {{host}}/v1/messages HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: test-key
anthropic-version: 2023-06-01

{
  "model": "qwen3.6:27b",
  "max_tokens": 256,
  "stream": true,
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Count from 1 to 5."}
  ]
}

###

### Messages with system prompt
POST {{host}}/v1/messages HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: test-key
anthropic-version: 2023-06-01

{
  "model": "qwen3.6:27b",
  "max_tokens": 256,
  "system": "You are a helpful assistant that speaks like a pirate.",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Say hello."}
  ]
}

###

### Messages with tools
POST {{host}}/v1/messages HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: test-key
anthropic-version: 2023-06-01

{
  "model": "qwen3.6:27b",
  "max_tokens": 512,
  "tools": [
    {
      "name": "get_weather",
      "description": "Get the weather for a location",
      "input_schema": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "location": {"type": "string"}
        }
      }
    }
  ],
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "What is the weather in Tokyo?"}
  ]
}

###

### Messages (no prefix)
POST {{host}}/messages HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: test-key
anthropic-version: 2023-06-01

{
  "model": "qwen3.6:27b",
  "max_tokens": 256,
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Say hello."}
  ]
}

###

### ─── Proxy ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Stats
GET {{host}}/stats HTTP/1.1
